30:48.180 --> 30:50.549
I'll be okay.

30:50.582 --> 30:53.152
The w-world.

30:53.185 --> 30:56.122
Just... live.

30:58.124 --> 31:01.060
Make good choices.

31:01.093 --> 31:03.329
Maybe things will
turn out different.

31:03.362 --> 31:05.331
Syd, I just...

31:05.364 --> 31:08.334
