helping him.

31:08.367 --> 31:11.337
I know.

31:11.370 --> 31:13.872
I shouldn't have asked.

31:25.884 --> 31:27.553
I'll miss you.

31:37.396 --> 31:40.399
Could we say good

31:50.409 --> 31:53.045
SYD:
Sometimes in a dream

31:53.079 --> 31:57.416
you remember you've had
this dream before.

32:02.921 --> 32:07.393
But that memory
is just part of the dream...

32:07.426 --> 32:12.131
the dream memory of a dream.

32:14.433 --> 32:19.305
When in truth, it's all really
happening for the first time...

32:19.338 --> 32:22.641
again.

32:29.615 --> 32:32.584
-Encoding perceptions.

32:32.618 --> 32:35.687
