33:00.979 --> 33:04.216
-Shh.

33:04.250 --> 33:05.484
PTONOMY:
Syd.

33:12.991 --> 33:16.495
What is happening to me?

33:24.170 --> 33:25.337
All I have are rumors, whispers.

33:25.371 --> 33:26.672
People go
to Admiral Fukyama's pedestal

33:26.705 --> 33:28.540
