41:17.042 --> 41:18.944
Hey!

41:20.979 --> 41:24.149
You made my friends sick.

41:28.219 --> 41:29.487
Yeah, hey.

41:29.521 --> 41:30.856
Hi, hi.

41:30.889 --> 41:34.025
Can you understand me?

41:34.059 --> 41:37.195
You picked a really shitty time
to attack us.

41:37.228 --> 41:39.130
I'm not saying it's your fault.

41:39.164 --> 41:40.832
I mean, it is, but...

41:40.866 --> 41:43.535
the timing, it's-it's not good.

41:43.569 --> 41:45.470
I'm dealing with a lot here.

41:45.503 --> 41:46.905
With the Shadow King.

41:46.938 --> 41:48.640
And, well, this...

41:48.674 --> 41:51.810
this isn't helping. So...

41:53.779 --> 41:54.880
I was hoping you could

41:54.913 --> 41:57.148
appreciate my situation

41:57.182 --> 42:00.218
and maybe, I don't know,

42:00.251 --> 42:03.221
be on your way.

42:03.254 --> 42:05.824
Go back to where you came fro--

42:05.857 --> 42:07.158
Otherwise, I have to kill you.

42:07.192 --> 42:09.227
Are you,
are you understanding this?

42:11.529 --> 42:13.832
Guess not.

42:48.099 --> 42:51.903
Remember,
I was gonna let you go.

43:09.187 --> 43:10.956
*

43:44.790 --> 43:47.325
NARRATOR:
So what have we learned?

43:47.358 --> 43:50.929
That a delusion is an idea.

43:50.962 --> 43:54.632
That an idea can be contagious.

43:54.666 --> 43:58.636
That human beings are
pattern-seeking animals.

43:58.670 --> 44:03.141
By which, I mean we prefer
ideas that fit a pattern.

44:03.174 --> 44:07.012
In other words,
we don't believe what we see.

44:07.045 --> 44:11.116
We see what we believe.

44:11.149 --> 44:13.618
And when we are stressed

44:13.651 --> 44:16.121
or our beliefs are challenged--

44:16.154 --> 44:18.223
when we feel threatened--

44:18.256 --> 44:23.628
the ideas we have
can become irrational,

44:23.661 --> 44:25.964
one delusion
leading to another,

44:25.997 --> 44:27.866
and another,

44:27.899 --> 44:32.904
as the human mind struggles
to maintain its identity.

44:32.938 --> 44:35.974
And when this occurs,

44:36.007 --> 44:38.076
what starts as an egg

44:38.109 --> 44:42.413
can become a monster.

